{"tid":714292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★CitiBank櫃員機出簡體字！ 職員稱一般只會顯示繁體中文或英文","createTime":"2018-06-23T14:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T07:28:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0f0eb43b3b6726a1948d3cd0b707bfed82b60dad","tid":714292,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"香港自動櫃員機用簡體字？真定假㗎？有網民在網上討論區貼文，指今晚(23日)7時半，在沙田廣場兩部CitiBank的自動櫃員機入卡，但在選擇中文服務後，卻顯示出一行不尋常的簡體字，寫道：「請輸入您的自动柜員机卡個人密碼，然後按輸入」。由於香港銀行甚少使用簡體字，未免令人感撲朔迷離。<br />\n<br />\n該名網民指，在輸入一半密碼後便感事有蹊蹺，遂即時退卡，並致電<span style=\"color: red;\">CitiBank熱線查詢，其職員稱一般櫃員機只會顯示繁體中文或英文</span>，他懷疑櫃員機是否被黑客入侵，也擔心其他人會受騙蒙遭受損失。<br />\n<br />\n該貼一出，旋即引起一片嘩然。有網民斷言，該部自動櫃員機一定有問題：「(正常顯示)吾(唔)會甘(咁)」；也有網民質疑，櫃員機或被做手腳，以盜取卡主密碼；有網民則建議事主即刻更改密碼。<br />\n<br />\n東網記者已聯絡CitiBank查詢事件，正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180623/photo/bkn-20180623202002655-0623_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180623212722\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180623%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180623202002655-0623_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180623212722&h=a2d1a28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180623/bkn-20180623202002655-0623_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180623%2Fbkn-20180623202002655-0623_00822_001.html&d=iGjqz4bTxluaHsUKAJ6OTtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=e32a4d8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180623/bkn-20180623202002655-0623_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bf00df7b4f00149fc115bf09ba3b6429355baf39","tid":714292,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\