同國家<br />\n可以搵人就住啲 system message code 翻譯過之後 import 入去個 software package<br />\n跟住真正嚮終端機 set deployment locale<br />\n咁而家有兩個問題<br />\n1. 套 software 已預備好簡體中文 resource <br />\n2. Deployment 嗰時 set 咗簡體"},{"pid":"ae9495e5896247e4097e7c1b6243499239288837","tid":714292,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T16:49:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> Hacked</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6513eaf4798f08f4783180ef67b78ff80e8cff5","tid":714292,"uid":119450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:05:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">CitiBank熱線查詢，其職員稱一般櫃員機只會顯示繁體中文或英文</span><br />\n<br />\n你打去熱線 點會識答呢啲IT狗問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1f96bd39219844c4266bb78a6507be7f52b974","tid":714292,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"CitiBank 正仆街黎<br />\n<br />\n原本仲諗住去開citigold<br />\n<br />\n依家唔駛啦, 屌佢老母"},{"pid":"8ba4e5dbe7a5b06bae4f6573959178d364bc0440","tid":714292,"uid":106848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a1f96bd39219844c4266bb78a6507be7f52b974","tid":714292,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"CitiBank 正仆街黎<br />\n<br />\n原本仲諗住去開citigold<br />\n<br />\n依家唔駛啦, 屌佢老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:21:38.000Z","msg":"之前諗住去開返個account<br />\n宜家可以慳返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbb3f54cb5f3073667606f4cd8ba7a1fc053798","tid":714292,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ba4e5dbe7a5b06bae4f6573959178d364bc0440","tid":714292,"uid":106848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a1f96bd39219844c4266bb78a6507be7f52b974","tid":714292,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"CitiBank 正仆街黎<br />\n<br />\n原本仲諗住去開citigold<br />